title: Garmin City Navigator North America NT 2014.20 Unlocked
description:
Garmin City Navigator North America NT 2014.20 Unlocked


Install the package running the CNNANT2014_20Update.msi file, the setup will install BaseCamp v4.2.2 and MapInstall v4.0.3 too:  replace the original exes with the patched ones.

Maps are already unlocked.

BaseCamp v4.2.2 Patched exe included.
MapInstall v4.0.3 Patched exe included

Starting from this release, the use of Mapsource is not recommended due to an incompatibility with the structure of the new maps.
The map obtained by that very outdated program may brik the new GPS, so you can continue to use it at your own risk; in this case test the map on a SD memory card, not in the GPS's internal memory.

Use MapInstall instead.
	

Have fun !!
